[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一下就变得灰蒙蒙的天空，雨滴丝丝缕缕落下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "该回去了啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女脸上浅浅的笑靥慢慢消逝。她怔怔看着屋檐外落下的雨滴，摊开掌心，外面的雨点落在手心的感觉冰冷湿润。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这场雨突如其来。像是她读过很多本有趣的故事一样，每本故事都是会有终局的，于是读书的乐趣便在翻到结尾的那一刻戛然而止。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而想到这里辰星便明白了一件事……她收回手掌轻轻按住自己的胸口……她不想就这么结束。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "蓦地身后脚步声响起，她转头回望，便见着分析员刚从店里取了把雨伞出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "玩累了吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "雨伞是我向店员借来的。不过我完全没想到，我只是去借会雨伞的功夫，辰星好像忽然变得消沉起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没有。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那你的表情……这算是疲惫，还是不开心？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我，我不是……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "辰星啊，有没有人跟你说过，你很不擅长撒谎。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看来还真给我猜对了，刚才不还挺好的吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我见她沉默，心下完全确定了猜想。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……分析员……是诈我……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "兵不厌诈嘛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我凝望着辰星，揣摩她的想法，而少女抿了抿粉色的唇，没能说话。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可当我要说什么时，辰星忽然抬起了头，认真看着我，咬着嘴唇开口了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我只是……不想这么快回去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她用细若蚊蚋般的声音念叨，我仔细盯着她发烫的耳垂，忽地有些奇妙的情绪在我胸口升腾。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "稳住有些加速的心跳，我走到她的面前。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我们是要回去，可在回去前，还有能体验的东西。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你上来吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我说着在辰星的面前半蹲下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "上……来？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是啊，上来，我背你。我和店员说好了，轮椅就放在这，明天我让其他人帮忙来取。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "雨中漫步，有试过吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没有……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那么，想试试吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
