        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "想……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女说着语气一顿，随后声音渐渐大了几分。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星云篆",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，我想试试。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我笑了笑，将伞递给辰星后，转过头去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那还愣着干嘛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我话音落下的时候，一团柔软就扑到了我的背后。",
